      "body" : "Another suggestion to ease chaining and eventually reduce the transmitted data is to specify a [json path](http://jsonpath.com/) to filter the output. For instance:\r\n```\r\nbitcoin-cli -rpcfilter '*.amount' listunspent\r\n```\r\nCompared to jq, it has the advantage of server side filtering. But I guess it is too much for core.",
